} with {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ {\b I}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i N}})}}{\fldrslt }}
} being an identity matrix of order {{\i N}} and {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ {\b M}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\u916*}})}}{\fldrslt }}
} a matrix with diagonal of {\u8722?1{\i s}} and a sub-diagonal of {1{\i s}} to the right. The transformation yields {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ {\u916*}{\i y}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i i}{\i t}})={\u945*}{\u916*}{\i y}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i i}{\i t}\u8722?1})+{\u946*}{\u916*}{\i x}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i i}{\i t}})+{\u916*}{\i v}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i i}{\i t}})}}{\fldrslt }}
