} in {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ {\u916*}{\i v}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i i}{\i t}})}}{\fldrslt }}
}, longer lags of the regressors are orthogonal to the error term and can be used as instruments (see 
(Roodman, {2009}
)) for additional details)}
